# Requirements Document Template

## Use Case
Generate requirements documentation during **Phase 1: Requirements Analysis** of the Aura Frog workflow. This template structures the analysis of user needs, functional requirements, non-functional requirements, and success criteria.

## Associated Phase
**Phase 1: Requirements Analysis (Understand)**

## When to Use
- At the beginning of any workflow
- When analyzing JIRA tickets or user requests
- Before technical planning begins
- To document scope and acceptance criteria

